modules.description: Processes DNS queries and constructs responses using strict protocol adherence. Operates on packet buffers, domain names, and resource records. Enables implementation of recursive DNS resolvers and authoritative name servers with zone overrides.

Provides functions for establishing TCP connections, sending and receiving DNS data over TCP, and setting up logging. Works with IP addresses, domain names, and DNS key structures. Used to build command-line tools for DNS query execution and configuration parsing.
